VIMOS Mask Preparation Software (VMMPS) is a copyright protected
software product of the European Southern Observatory, and provides a
tool to design masks for the VIMOS spectrograph MOS observations.
VMMPS is a Skycat plugin developed by Dario Bottini at the Istituto di
Fisica Cosmica G.Occhialini - CNR, Milano - Italy, in the framework of
the VIRMOS Consortium activities under ESO Contract
50979/INS/97/7569/GWI.

